  Week 2 Assignment

Welcome to the assignment for week #2. In this week, I want you to create a 30 second animatic for a film, commercial, or trailer. Here are the details:

  • Use ChatGPT to help with the concept and script
  • Use Midjourney to pull the images (don't forget to use our new prompting techniques)
  • Use VO tools to add narration or real-life VO to the film.
  • Add music and sound effects
  • Swap faces to keep the character consistent.
  • Create a moving face in D-ID.
  • Add a basic title
  • Upload your Assignment to the week #2 channel.
